35
00:03:34,262 --> 00:03:37,462
Don't tell me that the person who made this is...

36
00:03:37,462 --> 00:03:39,962
Of course, the master of tricks during the days of the Tokugawa Shogunate.

37
00:03:39,962 --> 00:03:43,362
Kichiemon Samizu, right?

38
