106
00:06:30,262 --> 00:06:31,962
so I win.

107
00:06:34,362 --> 00:06:36,262
Black-out?

108
00:06:36,262 --> 00:06:37,762
No need to fret.

109
00:06:37,762 --> 00:06:39,762
A black out was expected to begin with.

110
00:06:40,962 --> 00:06:43,462
Wind and rain, did someone open the window?

