157
00:08:53,162 --> 00:08:56,562
was set on to all the shutters of this building.

158
00:08:56,562 --> 00:08:58,762
Darn, that Thief Kid.

159
00:08:58,762 --> 00:09:01,462
He not only blacked the place out and threw us into the dark

160
00:09:01,462 --> 00:09:02,762
