165
00:09:13,162 --> 00:09:15,162
Get me a car.

166
00:09:15,162 --> 00:09:17,662
All the other remaining cars go after Thief Kid!

167
00:09:17,662 --> 00:09:20,362
He couldn't possibly use his hand glider in this typhoon,

168
