It's not poison.

174
00:09:38,562 --> 00:09:40,962
Look! It's a stun gun.

175
00:09:40,962 --> 00:09:43,962
It seems he was knocked out by this.

176
00:09:43,962 --> 00:09:45,662
I see.

177
00:09:45,662 --> 00:09:48,562
That guy decided to put this little one,

178
00:09:48,562 --> 00:09:51,162
