179
00:09:51,162 --> 00:09:52,162
Sorry.

180
00:09:52,162 --> 00:09:54,562
What do you mean, "I see".

181
00:09:54,562 --> 00:09:58,162
I mean, it's all because you went and publicized

182
00:09:58,162 --> 00:10:01,262
that jewelry that you just found last week to the media

183
00:10:01,262 --> 00:10:03,262
even before we completed preparing or tight security.

184
00:10:03,262 --> 00:10:04,962
That's why he walked off with the treasure.

185
00:10:04,962 --> 00:10:07,162
It was a month ago.

186
00:10:07,162 --> 00:10:09,862
I heard a month ago that the perfect amber,

187
00:10:09,862 --> 00:10:11,762
the giraffe's horns

188
00:10:11,762 --> 00:10:14,262
was laying asleep here at this temple.

189
00:10:14,262 --> 00:10:16,262
I had them change the date of publicizing

190
00:10:16,262 --> 00:10:19,362
