191
00:10:19,362 --> 00:10:21,262
I wanted him to think that this old man

192
00:10:21,262 --> 00:10:23,662
here got carried away at finding the perfect bait

193
00:10:23,662 --> 00:10:26,762
to capture that thief...

194
00:10:26,762 --> 00:10:28,962
Therefore, although security wasn't really prepared yet,

195
00:10:28,962 --> 00:10:31,762
I lead him to think that I accepted his challenge.

196
00:10:31,762 --> 00:10:35,462
Which means that the make-shift lighting...

197
00:10:35,462 --> 00:10:39,862
Right, I knew he would be causing a black-out.

198
00:10:39,862 --> 00:10:44,362
I also knew about that trick he used on the shutters.

199
00:10:44,362 --> 00:10:47,462
The electric current I rigged on the pedestals

200
00:10:47,462 --> 00:10:53,562
and calling the children were all strategies to lure him

201
00:10:53,562 --> 00:10:56,162
to coming to this temple.

202
00:10:56,162 --> 00:10:58,262
The lattice on the windows that with wood

203
00:10:58,262 --> 00:11:00,062
that looks worn out and easy to break.

204
00:11:00,062 --> 00:11:01,462
As well as the wall here that looks as if it would collapse

205
00:11:01,462 --> 00:11:02,662
