209
00:11:09,262 --> 00:11:11,762
and a sensor is built into it.

210
00:11:11,762 --> 00:11:13,562
If the door is forced open,

211
00:11:13,562 --> 00:11:17,162
a very noisy alarm is set to go off.

212
00:11:17,162 --> 00:11:19,362
But since there were no such sound,

213
00:11:19,362 --> 00:11:24,062
in other words, Thief Kid and his accomplices...

214
00:11:24,062 --> 00:11:27,662
are still in here.

215
00:11:27,662 --> 00:11:29,662
They are...

216
00:11:29,662 --> 00:11:31,362
The Thief Kid is still in here?

217
00:11:31,362 --> 00:11:32,462
Thief Kid?

218
00:11:45,326 --> 00:11:47,526
So, Inspector Nakamori,

219
00:11:47,526 --> 00:11:49,126
