220
00:11:49,126 --> 00:11:51,126
Check out all the faces of everyone here

221
00:11:51,126 --> 00:11:53,226
excluding the children and...

222
00:11:53,226 --> 00:11:55,826
There's something I'd like to make clear before that.

223
00:11:57,026 --> 00:11:59,826
Let me explain how Thief Kid took the amber horns

224
00:11:59,826 --> 00:12:03,026
from the statue of the giraffe.

225
00:12:03,026 --> 00:12:06,426
Just before the black-out, unless you insert

226
00:12:06,426 --> 00:12:10,126
and turn the white, black, red and green keys

227
00:12:10,126 --> 00:12:11,826
that you nailed onto the wall of this room of the pedestals

228
00:12:11,826 --> 00:12:16,826
that are in the four corners of the room

229
00:12:16,826 --> 00:12:19,426
at the same time...

230
00:12:20,626 --> 00:12:23,026
nobody could view the statue of the giraffe

231
00:12:23,026 --> 00:12:26,126
that is hidden in the pillar in the center.

232
00:12:26,126 --> 00:12:30,526
If by chance, Thief Kid got himself a spare somehow...

233
00:12:30,526 --> 00:12:31,826
How in the world did he, in the dark,

234
00:12:31,826 --> 00:12:33,626
where the pedestals nor the keyholes

