00:12:33,626 --> 00:12:36,126
were in view do what he did?

236
00:12:36,126 --> 00:12:39,926
As for light, the little ones had it on them, didn't they?

237
00:12:39,926 --> 00:12:42,526
The one on their watches!

238
00:12:42,526 --> 00:12:44,626
Since they said they would be guarding pedestal,

239
00:12:44,626 --> 00:12:47,426
Thief Kid probably used that light to do.

240
00:12:47,426 --> 00:12:49,726
We didn't turn on the light!

241
00:12:49,726 --> 00:12:51,826
It's true that we were covering the keyhole

242
00:12:51,826 --> 00:12:53,926
