243
00:12:53,926 --> 00:12:56,126
Because Ai told us not to turn on the light

244
00:12:56,126 --> 00:12:58,126
even if the lights went out.

245
00:12:58,126 --> 00:13:00,826
And, while you were covering the keyhole,

246
00:13:00,826 --> 00:13:02,426
